	   <tr><td colspan=2>Assuming comparable equipment...<br><br>Warrior Pros:<br><br>More HPs<br>Can do more Damage<br><br>Warrior Cons:<br><br>No utility<br>Not very good at taunting or keeping agro (you need to know how to use Taunt button AND you need to have very good procing weapons)<br><br>Shadow Knight Pros:<br><br>Much better Taunter<br>Better Utility (can FD, snare, has DoTs, can DA)<br><br>Shadow Knight Cons:<br><br>Lower damage output<br>Lower HPs<br><br><br><br><br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Thu Feb 13 21:21:14 2003</em><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
